                    <lb xml:id="uuid_4fab3535-b777-4ca6-a30b-a2fad0de30c2"/>exp. am 15.7.1927 <lb xml:id="uuid_bf5fd76a-8011-4515-87ae-93ff383bdb02"/>Dr.S/Ma</note>
